{"tid":96891,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大師 2017 年財運玄機系列","createTime":"2017-01-27T08:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T01:26:22.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3a93d1eb305faf69e20aeb43c8866767cb2d99","tid":96891,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"2017年財運玄機系列 <br />\n<br />\n沈大師：港股6月見頂\t宜急流勇退<br />\n2017/01/04 11:00<br />\n<br />\n「丙申猴年」快將完結，即將踏入的「丁酉雞年」，人稱沈大師的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈表示，按五行分析，丁屬火、酉屬金，兩者均利好股市，顯示股市會有升浪，但丁火力量略不足。<br />\n<br />\n未來一年港股都是靠內地資金「北水南調」幫助，但不可預期力度會太大，投資上要懂得在高位急流勇退。<br />\n<br />\n整體上，他預期2017年上半年股市表現較好，全年高位料於6月出現，最遲7月會有見頂跡象。<br />\n<br />\n沈大師預期雞年股市流年運程如下（按新曆）<br />\n<br />\n2017年2月至2017年4月：見反覆，有機會試底。<br />\n2017年5月至2017年7月：有大升浪，高位料於6月出現，最遲7月亦見頂。<br />\n2017年8月至2017年10月：反覆向下走。<br />\n2017年11月至2018年1月：尋底格局。<br />\n<br />\n三大投資建議<br />\n（1）以保守為原則，如能遇上高位謹記適時急流勇退。<br />\n（2）3月至4月為入市佳期。<br />\n（3）8月前走貨為上策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7285\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2FVip%2Fdetail%3Fid%3D7285&d=9qXlY%2BjSbx5suXWKSvYojZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5e53d2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7285</a>"},{"pid":"579b0ff08b0c3a97c59eddaeace1cb4143817586","tid":96891,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"2017年財運玄機系列 <br />\n<br />\n沈大師：2017年樓市真跌 小心假陽春<br />\n2017/01/05 10:01<br />\n<br />\n人稱沈大師的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈之前預測猴年運程時，已預期香港樓市於2016年有開始回落的跡象，但真正大跌則見於2017年、2018年，尤其是「丁酉雞年」的立春八字中，不帶一點土，意味雞年會有比較急速的下跌情況。<br />\n<br />\n全年而言，大師預計2017年樓市會出現「驚嚇現象」。以新曆計，2017年5月至7月，樓市仍能勉強有支持，但承接力明顯轉弱；到8月立秋後：因改行金水大運，土則無支持，所以樓市會急轉直下，料未來一年至一年半樓價至少跌30%至40%，但最大跌幅應會在2018年時發生。<br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n（1）2017年可能時而有些季節性因素令樓市出現少許好轉的假象，切勿輕舉妄動。<br />\n（2）受樓市下行影響，地產股及收租股表現都較不理想，股民應避免沾手這兩類型的股份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2FVip%2Fdetail%3Fid%3D7316&d=9qXlY%2BjSbx5suXWKSvYojZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a06b95f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7316</a>"},{"pid":"6d7f9dc4cd8d882aa0cb56f0e8cd6bf312c3d283","tid":96891,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"2017年財運玄機系列 <br />\n<br />\n沈大師：\t金價料大升 年初低吸等收成<br />\n2017/01/06 17:05<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商品範圍廣泛，包括能源、金屬、農產品等，訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈認為不能一概而論。正如他之前預測猴年商品市場時，曾呼籲要留意屬「火」的元素，例如油價會升，金屬類商品亦都會升。<br />\n<br />\n不過，即將來臨的雞年，沈振盈預期商品市場情況有變，三大主流商品走勢預測如下：<br />\n<br />\n（1）能源：大師預期油價波動不大，僅處每桶55美元左右水平徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n（2）金屬：銅、鐵、鋁三者有升浪，5月至中秋期間為高峰；金價更料有急速上升之勢，建議投資者可於年初金價約每盎斯1,140美元或更低位時，可多儲黃金。<br />\n<br />\n（3）農產品：只有首季是佳境，料其餘三季均無大作為<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2FVip%2Fdetail%3Fid%3D7379&d=9qXlY%2BjSbx5suXWKSvYojZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b5a261b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=7379</a>"},{"pid":"35a294121657615dcfaf53d5569176377034dbb4","tid":96891,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街，開地圖炮。"},{"pid":"103831b1cfa7272a0d2cc2be5cf92bede92015f9","tid":96891,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"//已預期香港樓市於2016年有開始回落的跡象，但真正大跌則見於2017年、2018年//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n師傅由2010年已經唱淡<br />\n原來2017年2018年先開始大跌<br />\n<br />\n如果有D傻鳩真係聽師父講<br />\n2010年就賣樓<br />\n結果2018年先大跌<br />\n咁個8年升幅真係揼春囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5391d1c833f0ea501e173e692ad47de7ea5a82","tid":96891,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"師父臨過年先使出「五行測市」大絕，仲以為佢唔記得點用𠻹"},{"pid":"d607fb4a0256ec3d05e5bc666fdf70d47e97436f","tid":96891,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>//已預期香港樓市於2016年有開始回落的跡象，但真正大跌則見於2017年、2018年//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n師傅由2010年已經唱淡<br />\n原來2017年2018年先開始大跌<br />\n<br />\n如果有D傻鳩真係聽師父講<br />\n2010年就賣樓<br />\n結果2018年先大跌<br />\n咁個8年升幅真係揼春囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師父續年計嘅<br />\n有一年跌就可以正如筆者所說！"},{"pid":"84be381337a46f9665af9457c1cf2a551d9b474c","tid":96891,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/91231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F91231b.jpg&h=c9f42e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/981125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F981125.jpg&h=af2464e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/929c7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F929c7e.jpg&h=5d808d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/5aba31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F5aba31.jpg&h=5f359a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2e8691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2e8691.jpg&h=75b7357f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/944bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F944bb2.jpg&h=f1cdf002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/29be46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F29be46.jpg&h=7f7e7457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/da0997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fda0997.jpg&h=527955e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"613e973c2bc8241bc509d897960d76b4271ea955","tid":96891,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結果</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/e5f11c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fe5f11c.jpg&h=59fae5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n某年某月某日：<br />\n筆者最感驕傲的是，多年來憑著獨立思考，一直力排眾議，苦口婆心的勸說大家要小心樓市爆破，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">看！正如筆者所說，現今樓價已跌超過五成，現在回到五萬元一呎了！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/bfc828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fbfc828.jpg&h=d3ef3fdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2be8e5c2a79307bd6b19277ae9b5157d48ea1510","tid":96891,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"師父成名絕招之一<br />\n係黃金金價<br />\n果然今年年尾<br />\n師父始終都技癢<br />\n要露兩手黃金絕活比街坊開下眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbd089beace61a7d3dbc805c695b07764ce69a9","tid":96891,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"2017年11月至2018年1月：尋底格局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}